# BEAT

BEAT is an acronym for "**B**erlin **E**lektronisches **A**udio **T**üfteln", or in English:  "**B**erlin **E**lectronic **A**udio **T**inkering", and is an event about exactly that.  BEAT takes place every second Monday of a month from 19:00 aboard the [c-base](https://c-base.org).

